From 3f99337803142cf7d21853a86d9f4b2d3a636300 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: esp-glow firmware <firmware@esp-glow.local>
Date: Sat, 11 Jul 2026 13:41:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] F1: DMX output path + render task + host-tested render-pacing

- render_pacing.{h,cpp}: pure paceNextFrame() (tick->seconds, drift-correcting
  deadline math). Behind frames rebase off now (no catch-up burst).
- test_render_pacing.cpp: 9 tests (steady state, drift, u64 wrap safety, zero
  period). Wired into 'make test'.
- dmx_sink.{h,cpp}: filled scaffold. begin() installs esp_dmx driver + pins;
  send() forces start code 0x00, writes 512 slots, dmx_send + dmx_wait_send.
- firmware/main/render_task.{h,cpp}: FreeRTOS task pinned to core 1 at 44 Hz,
  delegates pacing to glow::paceNextFrame, logs per-5s stats.
- firmware/main/main.cpp: F1 hardcoded patch (1ch dimmer @ u0/base0, 50%
  DimmerEffect) driving the render task into DmxSink.
- firmware/main/idf_component.yml: espressif/esp_dmx + littlefs deps.

Host make test: all green (incl. 9 new render_pacing tests).
